Text Classification Model for AG News Dataset using Bag of Words (BOW) and Naive Bayes coded

Here is a link to the text classification model that I created in google colab:
https://colab.research.google.com/drive/1-iKZfR04NH9xxVwom4ugkY07OdQFtZuz?usp=sharing

Runtime is approximately 1 minute. 
Categorizes a given news headline into one of four categories (world, sports, business, sci/tech) with precision of around 87%.
Trained on 96,000 headlines and tested on 24,000 headlines. 80/20 train test split.


